page.title: 06BUILDINGS 2
page.content: The roof of Rose Cottage is low pitched,there are slates on the roof, not tiles. The brick pattern is { {"Stretcher Bond,"}and there are two storeys in the house. Fingle Cottage has a high tiled pitched roof and{"Flemish Bond"}brick walls. The house has two storeys and beams. Verela cottage has a high pitched tiled roof and the brick pattern of the walls is{"Stretcher {Bond."}The house is two storeys high. One house looks like a bungalow but it is a house with rooms in the roof. The tiles are old .
